Class IIDImpl

    public class IIDImpl
extends SFImpl
implements IID
    An implementation of the model object 'IID'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Con Data1
    • XBase
    • YBase
    • XUnits
    • YUnits
    • XSize
    • YSize
    • Con Data2
    • XC Size D
    • YC Size D
    • Con Data3
    • Color
